Hello T206 Group:

Is anyone looking to move any of the following (mostly) commons?

  * Ames (Hands At Chest)
  * Ames (Hands Above Head)
  * Ames (Portrait)
  * Bridwell (Portrait -- No Cap)
  * Donlin (With Bat)
  * Doyle, Larry (Throwing)
  * Doyle, Larry (With Bat)
  * Durham
  * Marquard (Pitching) [HOF, obviously]
  * McCormick
  * Murray (Batting)
  * Tenney


Willing to pay PPGS. Thank you in advance! -- Rick
